(firstQuint)Efficacy and Safety of Zingiber Officinale Roscoe Extract on Body Fat.

 This study was a 12 weeks, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled human trial.

 Forty subjects were randomly divided into Zingiber officinale Roscoe extract 200 mg or 400 mg or placebo group.

 The investigators measured Body Fat Mass, Percent Body Fat, Fat Free Mass, weight, and body mass index.

